  Clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: c3d062ba890d76a4184b395f28822a16, type: 3}
  Subtitles: "Oh my gosh you won\u2019t believe what happened to my friend Chrissy,
    the one that\u2019s a truck driver and also just happens to be half-robot? This
    one dude at her job keeps asking if she needs extra oil when he\u2019s doing
    refills and I mean yeah sure, sometimes she says yes, but like\u2026 Isn\u2019t
    that like super robo-phobic??? It\u2019s almost like he thinks all robots drink
    motor oil or something, which is like wow\u2026 Like you see what I mean right?
    Do you think she should be contacting HR about this?"
